            <h4>Customizing your Groupstore tab</h4>
                    1. Go to your Groupstore tab on your facebook profile
                    <br />
                    2. Click on "Custom message", which is right below the Event description.  There you can write a custom message about your event.
                    <br />
                    3. Click "Show/Hide" goals.  This is for those fundraising money.  Here you can set your fundraising goal.
                    (You should then see the change reflected on your thermometer)
                    <br />
                    4. Other things can do is - 
                        <ul>
                            <li>Check your sales - See who's bought/donated on your Groupstore.</li>                            
                            <li>View External link - The link to send to people who are not on Facebook</li>
                            <li>Share Button - Shares your Groupstore tab by posting a message on your Facebook Wall.  This is the best way to promote your fundraiser.</li>
                        </ul>
